name: Mackin
origin: Astronaut-named feature, Apollo 17 site. (Spelling changed from Mackin-Apollo.)

name: Guang Han Gong
origin: Moon palace where Chang-E and Yutu lived in Chinese mythology.

name: Statio Tianhe
origin: Ancient Chinese name for the Milky Way, a sky river that separates Niulang and Zhinyu in the Chinese folk tale “The Cowherd and the Weaver Girl.”
